    <item>
      <title>Use IFTTT to send currency exchange rate mail daily</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/doc/ifttt/ifttt-send-currency-exchange-rate-mail/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/doc/ifttt/ifttt-send-currency-exchange-rate-mail/</guid>
      <description>
        
          
            &lt;h2 id=&#34;requirement&#34;&gt;Requirement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I want to have daily mail including currency exchange rate information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mail subject: include the exchange rate in the mail subject.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mail content:
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has some links to banks&#39; exchange rate pages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Include some exchange rate history charts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use &lt;a href=&#34;https://ifttt.com/&#34;&gt;ifttt.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a new Applet on IFTTT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add a new &amp;quot;If This&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-8.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-8.png?w=605&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-432&#34; width=&#34;382&#34; height=&#34;180&#34;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose &amp;quot;finance&amp;quot; service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image.png?w=811&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-416&#34; width=&#34;446&#34; height=&#34;274&#34;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose &amp;quot;Today&#39;s exchange rate report&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-1.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-1.png?w=1024&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-418&#34; width=&#34;568&#34; height=&#34;280&#34;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose the input/output currency and trigger time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-2.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://dennys.files.wordpress.com/2022/03/image-2.png?w=702&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-420&#34; width=&#34;385&#34; height=&#34;373&#34;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          
          
        
      </description>
